description:
In episode 775, Jack and Miles are joined by performer Connor Del Rio to discuss Florida agents raiding a Covid-19 data scientists home, California considering changing police officer job requirements, the Covid-19 vaccine going out, why we need to be calling what Trump is doing a coup, Israel claiming aliens are hiding until we are ready, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Fired COVID-19 data scientist posts video of Florida agents raiding her home: "They pointed guns at my kids"
  2. Democrats to DeSantis: Rescind job offer to coronavirus conspiracy theorist
  3. Did COVID data whistleblower hack Florida’s emergency alert system? Police raid home
  4. California considers requiring police officers be over 25 or have bachelor's degree
  5. COVID-19 VACCINE WILLIAM SHAKESPEARE AT FRONT OF THE LINE... First Shots Given!!!
  6. Willingness to get COVID-19 vaccine up 13 points since September: Gallup
  7. Find Your Place in the Vaccine Line
  8. ‘This Must Be Your First’
  9. Arizona Republican Party Now Calling on Voters to Fight and Die For Trump’s Election War
  10. Aliens in hiding until mankind is ready, says ex-Israeli space head
  11. WATCH: Ruthven - Evil
